.Dt RBATCHIPD 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm rbatchipd
.Nd AWS Batch multi-node parallel hosts IP daemon
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility retrieves the
.Ev AWS_BATCH_JOB_ID
from
.NM rbatchip .
It's primary function is to colect the IP addresses of the AWS Batch
compute nodes, so as to be able to build an MPI hosts file.
